name: Bristles - The Good Life
description:
On the coast near idyllic Margaret River in Western Australia’s South West wine region lies Prevelly, a tiny townsite situated next to the mouth of the river. Prevelly is a microcosm of the laid back surfing and artistic lifestyle of the region where everyone knows each other and a surf before work is the norm.

Original photography filtered through the lens of generative abstraction. Digital oil painted onto a noisy geometric canvas. 6000x6000. Made in Processing.
